    },
    {
        title: "D-Kanto Admins | Admin Dashboard",
        body: "Admin Dashboard created to manage the products of D-Kanto's website. In this project admins can create, update, delete, look for and filter the products. I continue pushing me hard to improve this website and rise my knowledge. It also have a pagination method and light and dark theme. What I liked the most of developing this site was to create the preview of the products.",
        image: "../../images/d-kanto-admin.png",
        repository: "https://github.com/CarMi0Proggramer/d-kanto-admin",
        preview: "https://d-kanto-admin.onrender.com",
        skills: [
            {
                name: "HTML5",
                path: "../../svgs/html.svg",
            },
            {
